To run the tests:

1) create a test PostgreSQL database (default: meqaris-test running locally),

2) set a password if required (default: meqaris01),

3) allow some user to connect to the database (default: meqaris),

4) run
	./test-suite.sh

  or

	make check

  (from the top directory).

Consult the code in 'test-func.bash' to change the defaults if needed.
